tourBios.carHigh:
2014: Shot rounds of 71-73-74-70 to make his first cut of the PGA TOUR China Series' season, a T18 at the United Investment Real Estate Wuhan Open…Withdrew in the second round at the Earls Beijing Open due to injury…Made the cut in his final three starts—at the Nine Dragons Open (66th), the Hainan Open (T39) and the Tour Championship presented by CTS Tycoon (T24). 
2013: Played on the weekend at the European Challenge Tour's Foshan Open. Opened 76-72 before faltering over his final 36 holes, shooting 78-84 to T65.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was T18th in 2014 at the United Investment Real Estate Wuhan Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T51st in Par 3 Birdie or Better Leaders on the PGA Tour China Series.
